<blockquote class="uncited"><div>Hi all,<br><br><br>Looking for a GUI to use with LÖVE2D, what's current status on this one ? Thanks in advance !</div></blockquote>Well I would say that it works quite well and it's pretty stable and functional now. But be aware that it's a GUI mostly intended for tools/editors creation, not really for in-game elements. You can still tweak it for this purpose but it's clearly not its best usage.<br><br>And the biggest issue is still the lack of documentation, the best way to work with it is to have the imgui.h file opened and use it as your reference.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://love2d.org/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=134317">Fenrir</a> — Thu Aug 10, 2017 6:14 am</p><hr />
